# ── Railway frontend service — build-time environment variables ────────────────
# Copy the variable below into the Railway static service's "Variables" panel
# BEFORE triggering a build.  Vite inlines VITE_* variables at build time, so
# changing this value requires a rebuild of the frontend service.
#
# Set VITE_API_URL to the public URL Railway assigns to the API service.
# Example: https://mathforces-api.up.railway.app
# No trailing slash.
VITE_API_URL=
